# PyGUI

A simple Python GUI extension.  
Build easy GUI apps with PySide6 â€” lightweight and ready to extend.

## Features

- Simple GUI window with label  
- Easy to run with a single class  
- Packaged for easy installation via pip  
- Built on PySide6 for cross-platform support

## Installation

Install with pip:

```bash
pip install pygui
